{
  "stem": "20710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we used to, you know, all have a few, a few spoons of soup or whatever the, you know, to just to be able to survive.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But after a few-- yeah, once a week, during the night, he used to, you know, let us come out of this, of this bunker, and to come into this barn there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then there was an attic to go up there and catch a little bit fresh air, because there was a time we couldn't-- there was not-- there was no air there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I know either once a week or twice a week, but then it came to a point that-- I mean, I'm talking about myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I couldn't anymore, because my legs were so-- they were like rubber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I, I-- my muscles had-- they didn't function.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We couldn't stretch out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were just sitting, like in one position.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About eight, I think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, we used to go up-- yeah, we used to go up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't know, once in two, three days, or whatever, where we couldn't anymore, you know, hold back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was going on for a month.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in between, in between this month that we were hiding there-- so all these people who came to the ghetto, I think, maybe a couple of weeks later they surrounded the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they cleaned out maybe half.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took away my mother at that time, my father, and my oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, no, my oldest brother was with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm sorry, with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they put them on a train, and they took them away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I remember this woman who used to make-- bring us down the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she told us that they, they took away all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
